        <updateDate>2019-08-01T21:20:59Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Surveillance and Testing of Opioids to Prevent Fentanyl Deaths Act of 2018 or the STOP Fentanyl Deaths Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill establishes and expands programs to support increased detection and monitoring of fentanyl and other synthetic opioids, and also establishes a pilot program for point-of-use testing of illicit drugs for dangerous contaminants.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
